Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.55,0:01:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是屬於他的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.12,0:01:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於他來說最好的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.33,0:01:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能使他安心的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:01:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對小月來說也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.63,0:02:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.84,0:02:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎 歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.74,0:02:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋刀魚 一條30日元 兩條50日元
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.84,0:02:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來點嗎 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.35,0:02:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.35,0:02:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多送給小姑娘一條
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃些 早點長大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.75,0:02:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏「球棒少年」是不會出現的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.24,0:02:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.94,0:02:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會保護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只會保護小月的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.12,0:03:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為麻洛美已經不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把麻洛美拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在全國突然出現的神秘黑色物質
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勢力正急劇擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並席捲各地 造成重大損失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經無法阻止它的成長了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷺月子 你在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 月子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:03:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHO-P
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.35,0:04:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終回。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你SHO-P
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親怎能只給自己買香煙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香煙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.22,0:04:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 還是沒戒掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吸MILD SEVEN來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.03,0:05:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組長 能聽到嗎 組長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那裏吧 組長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.83,0:05:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和月子在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.14,0:05:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬庭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 把月子還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去麻洛美後的人們內心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使「球棒少年」無限成長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打倒那傢伙 一定要鷺月子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了嗎 組長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻洛美和「球棒少年」一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們的根源都是月子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻洛美原本是月子的小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是由於月子不小心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天把麻洛美…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼「球棒少年」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西根本不會出現在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:05:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察先生把有害電波消滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是警察 真是為咱老百姓辦實事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗布
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血壓下降
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸血 趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 她不可能在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.84,0:06:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 再來一杯啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.95,0:06:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不要多喝為好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛啊 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長得不像老爹 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將來一定是日本第一的大美人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啤酒來了 讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贈送的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作很累吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.64,0:07:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了豬狩先生最喜歡的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美佐江
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美 快來這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在那兒那麼親熱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美佐江
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是心有點慌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你會晚回家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎樣進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把老公還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.95,0:07:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏不是你應該存在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小月 快帶父親逃跑 快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 老公
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼會跟來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 麻洛美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.35,0:08:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用勉強自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廟會 工作本來就很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是兩回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我想有個女兒來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直和老爸相處不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想和自己的兒子也那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.63,0:09:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪嗎 我說這些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.43,0:09:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是個女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 孩子 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受現實吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有你在身邊就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我不在了 就不用這麼痛苦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許再說那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是想逃避罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為逃避就能得救的想法只是幻想而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有多痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:09:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都要正視現實 並一起熬過去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美佐江
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.85,0:10:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前 想和你道別
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我非常熟悉的你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 非常明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美佐江
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心肺停止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心臟按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是你的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 我當然明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世界滿是謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:11:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.94,0:11:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個個都這麼胡鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 這裏可是屬於你的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的世界會消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗不要總說個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的歸宿早就不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去歸宿的現實才是我真正的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組長回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬庭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.23,0:12:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.03,0:12:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉要AA制了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.14,0:12:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是因為月子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「球棒少年」是月子十年前製造出來的妄想的產物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她讓那個東西在現代復活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令事態擴大到如此地步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小月沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.15,0:12:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯的是它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.42,0:12:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是「球棒少年」的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清醒吧 麻洛美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.33,0:13:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的死是月子造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十年前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是小學生的你遭到道路魔的襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.35,0:13:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在帶著寵物狗麻洛美散步的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.52,0:13:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿著溜冰鞋 手持金屬球棒的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方的搜查也是一無所獲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有抓到犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為從一開始就根本不存在道路魔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為你自己的不小心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬆開了麻洛美的繩索
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果麻洛美被飛馳而過的汽車碾死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒敢告訴父親這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你害怕被責罵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.83,0:14:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以編造了什麼道路魔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了把自己裝扮成受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的被打了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的父親全部都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.15,0:14:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為了你 裝作到處尋找犯人的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是因為他對你過分嚴厲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造成你性格內向 他很為此而自責
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 這裏面包含著他對你的補償
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及對你能承認錯誤的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬庭 後面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.84,0:14:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算合為一體了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:15:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論你多麼強大都是個騙局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.35,0:15:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洞察真相之劍的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬庭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.13,0:15:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起來 快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:15:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小月 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 就因為一隻狗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世界還真不爭氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的死是月子造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為你自己的不小心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.77,0:16:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬆開了麻洛美的繩索
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果麻洛美被飛馳而過的汽車碾死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒敢告訴父親這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你害怕被責罵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.35,0:16:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以編造了什麼道路魔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了把自己裝扮成受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻洛美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻洛美 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:16:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:17:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.34,0:17:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了 麻洛美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.05,0:18:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才讓父親買給你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕父親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻洛美 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.82,0:19:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是 戰後一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東京都復興實行委員會宣佈重建完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東京已經從兩年前的悲劇中完全復興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.74,0:21:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說東京已經復興了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我們公司還遠沒有復興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.65,0:21:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次以後 那個計劃完全不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那部是動畫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一般的電影不同嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是唯獨狗不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那主人可煩人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是忙得不可開交
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.84,0:21:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和芙雅一起呼嚕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然這消息就給別家了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.92,0:24:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢告
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.22,0:24:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像快要結束的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.79,0:24:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪迴過後又是開始
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.93,0:24:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撿起基石堆積起來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.93,0:24:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,循環往復的無限體
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.34,0:24:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有解不開的謎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.14,0:24:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解不開的迷沒有答案
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.64,0:24:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.81,0:24:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見

